# 📊 Sales Performance Analysis | Power BI  

This project focuses on analyzing **sales performance** using the Superstore dataset. It provides insights into sales trends, product performance, and profitability across different regions and time periods.  

---

## 🚀 Project Objectives  
- Track **monthly, quarterly, and yearly sales performance**.  
- Identify **top-performing products, categories, and regions**.  
- Measure **profit margins and sales growth trends**.  
- Provide **recommendations** to improve business decisions.  

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Skills Used  
- **Power BI** → Dashboards, KPIs, DAX calculations  
- **Data Cleaning & Transformation** → Preparing raw Superstore dataset  
- **Data Analysis** → Sales trends, profitability analysis, customer insights  
- **Business Intelligence** → Storytelling with data  

---

## 🔑 Key Insights  
- The **top region** consistently outperformed others in sales contribution.  
- Certain **categories and sub-categories** drove strong sales but showed **low profit margins**.  
- Seasonal trends highlighted peaks in **quarterly and yearly sales cycles**.  
- Insights were used to recommend strategies for **profit optimization and customer targeting**.  

---

✨ This project demonstrates how raw sales data can be turned into **actionable business intelligence** using **Power BI**.  
